    unique challenges and opportunities within the web3 space. What we're
    offering is more than just another program; it's a roadmap tailored for Web3
    projects.
  </p>
  <div
    class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row items-stretch justify-start gap-6 md:gap-32 w-full"
